title: Il Divo - The Greatest Hits [Deluxe Edition] 2-CD Set 2012
description:
Source: 2012 CD

Il Divo - The Greatest Hits [Deluxe Edition] 2-CD Set 320cbr (Big Papi) 2012 



By TEA

This is a truly a great collection of Il Divo and what they have worked on for over eight years. Song after Song these wonderful passioned singers perform great songs in the way only IL Divo can. If this is your first CD of theres you will be amazed, if your a long time fan like me you will still love it and want this collection. There are four new songs on this greatest hits collection too all done with voices that are truly wonderful. If you ever get a chance to see these guys live it will be a concert that will stay with you forever they are the best live performing group ever I saw. Truly amazing voices and a great CD for everyone to enjoy! A must have gift for yourself or for others!
